porn%20over%20four%20years.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnJacob%20Walden%2C%2038%2C%20is%20an%20executive%20and%20co-owner%20of%20Emerald%20Healthcare%2C%20a%20Woodmere-based%20company%20that%20oversees%20assisted%20living%20and%20nursing%20homes%20around%20the%20US.%20He%20was%20remanded%20to%20a%20federal%20jail%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAt%20his%20arraignment%20at%C2%A0Central%20Islip%20Federal%20Court%2C%20Walden%20entered%20a%20not-guilty%20plea%20to%20a%20six-count%20indictment%20that%20charged%20him%20with%20sexually%20exploiting%20two%20teens%2C%20ages%2016%20and%2017%2C%20as%20well%20as%20receiving%20and%20possessing%20child%20pornography%2C%20reported%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2025%2F01%2F22%2Fus-news%2Fnassau-county-health-executive-jacob-walden-accused-of-preying-on-teen-girls-to-produce-child-porn%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BAs%20alleged%2C%20the%20defendant%20enticed%20minors%20to%20produce%20sexually%20explicit%20photographs%20and%20videos%20of%20themselves%20and%20send%20them%20to%20him%20via%20the%20Internet%20in%20exchange%20for%20payment.%20Protecting%20children%20from%20predators%20who%20sexually%20exploit%20them%20will%20always%20be%20a%20priority%20of%20my%20Office%2C%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0US%20Attorney%20John%20Durham%2C%20of%20the%20Eastern%20District%20of%20New%20York%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnProsecutors%20said%20Jacob%20Walden%2C%20a%20married%20man%20and%20father%20of%20five%2C%20bought%20at%20least%20500%20images%20and%205%2C000%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20videos%20from%20a%20massive%20production%20and%20distribution%20network%20that%20catered%20to%20adult%20male%20buyers%20in%20the%20US%20and%20aboard.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThey%20also%20claimed%20that%20Walden%20encouraged%20minors%20to%20take%20sexual%20photos%20of%20themselves%20by%20engaging%20in%20sexually%20explicit%20online%20chats%20with%20them%20via%20social%20media%20and%20encrypted%20messaging%20systems.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnJacob%20Walden%20was%20arrested%20on%20July%2031%2C%202024.%20He%20was%20placed%20under%20home%20confinement%20at%20his%20Valley%20Stream%20home%2C%20with%20limitations%20imposed%20on%20his%20use%20of%20technological%20devices%20and%20interactions%20with%20children.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20accused%20broke%20his%20terms%20within%20a%20month%20of%20his%20arrest%20after%20he%20made%20an%20unscheduled%20stop%20at%20a%20Verizon%20store%20and%20offered%20a%20lady%20money%20for%20sex%20on%20WhatsApp.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20law%20enforcement%20officials%2C%20Walden%20is%20currently%20being%20held%20at%20the%20Metropolitan%20Detention%20Center%20in%20Brooklyn%20without%20bail%20until%20his%20trial%20after%20prosecutors%20claimed%20he%20poses%20a%20risk%20of%20escape%20and%20is%20a%20danger%20to%20society.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHis%20next%20court%20date%20is%20February%2024.%20If%20found%20guilty%2C%20he%20may%20spend%20up%20to%2030%20years%20behind%20bars%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737658680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-02%2Froe31vpg_us-court-pixabay_625x300_23_February_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjacob-walden-emerald-healthacre-us-healthcare-executive-father-of-5-charged-with-producing-child-pornography-7538756%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jacob%20Walden%20is%20an%20executive%20and%20co-owner%20of%20Emerald%20Healthcare%2C%20a%20Woodmere-based%20company%20that%20oversees%20assisted%20living%20and%20nursing%20homes%20around%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjacob-walden-emerald-healthacre-us-healthcare-executive-father-of-5-charged-with-producing-child-pornography-7538756%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBlatantly%20Unconstitutional%26quot%3B%3A%20Judge%20Blocks%20Trump%20Citizenship%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20judge%20in%20Seattle%20on%20Thursday%20blocked%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration%20from%20implementing%20an%20executive%20order%20curtailing%20the%20right%20to%20automatic%20birthright%20citizenship%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bblatantly%20unconstitutional.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.S.%20District%20Judge%20John%20Coughenour%20at%20the%20urging%20of%20four%20Democratic-led%20states%20issued%20a%20temporary%20restraining%20order%20preventing%20the%20administration%20from%20enforcing%20the%20order%2C%20which%20the%20Republican%20president%20signed%20on%20Monday%20during%20his%20first%20day%20on%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20blatantly%20unconstitutional%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20told%20a%20lawyer%20with%20the%20U.S.%20Justice%20Department%20defending%20Trump's%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20has%20already%20become%20the%20subject%20of%20five%20lawsuits%20by%20civil%20rights%20groups%20and%20Democratic%20attorneys%20general%20from%2022%20states%2C%20who%20call%20it%20a%20flagrant%20violation%20of%20the%20U.S.%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20this%20order%2C%20babies%20being%20born%20today%20don't%20count%20as%20U.S.%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20Washington%20Assistant%20Attorney%20General%20Lane%20Polozola%20told%20Senior%20U.S.%20District%20Judge%20John%20Coughenour%20at%20the%20start%20of%20a%20hearing%20in%20Seattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolozola%20-%20on%20behalf%20of%20Democratic%20state%20attorneys%20general%20from%20Washington%20state%2C%20Arizona%2C%20Illinois%20and%20Oregon%20-%20urged%20the%20judge%20to%20issue%20a%20temporary%20restraining%20order%20to%20prevent%20the%20administration%20from%20carrying%20out%20this%20key%20element%20of%20Trump's%20immigration%20crackdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challengers%20argue%20that%20Trump's%20action%20violates%20the%20right%20enshrined%20in%20the%20citizenship%20clause%20of%20the%20Constitution's%2014th%20Amendment%20that%20provides%20that%20anyone%20born%20in%20the%20United%20States%20is%20a%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20in%20his%20executive%20order%20directed%20U.S.%20agencies%20to%20refuse%20to%20recognize%20the%20citizenship%20of%20children%20born%20in%20the%20United%20States%20if%20neither%20their%20mother%20nor%20father%20is%20a%20U.S.%20citizen%20or%20legal%20permanent%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20brief%20filed%20late%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20U.S.%20Justice%20Department%20called%20the%20order%20an%20%26quot%3Bintegral%20part%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20president's%20efforts%20%26quot%3Bto%20address%20this%20nation's%20broken%20immigration%20system%20and%20the%20ongoing%20crisis%20at%20the%20southern%20border.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20filed%20in%20Seattle%20has%20been%20progressing%20more%20quickly%20than%20the%20four%20other%20cases%20brought%20over%20the%20executive%20order.%20It%20has%20been%20assigned%20to%20Coughenour%2C%20an%20appointee%20of%20Republican%20former%20President%20Ronald%20Reagan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20potentially%20could%20rule%20from%20the%20bench%20after%20hearing%20arguments%2C%20or%20he%20could%20wait%20to%20write%20a%20decision%20ahead%20of%20Trump's%20order%20taking%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20order%2C%20any%20children%20born%20after%20Feb.%2019%20whose%20mothers%20or%20fathers%20are%20not%20citizens%20or%20lawful%20permanent%20residents%20would%20be%20subject%20to%20deportation%20and%20would%20be%20prevented%20from%20obtaining%20Social%20Security%20numbers%2C%20various%20government%20benefits%20and%20the%20ability%20as%20they%20get%20older%20to%20work%20lawfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20150%2C000%20newborn%20children%20would%20be%20denied%20citizenship%20annually%20if%20Trump's%20order%20is%20allowed%20to%20stand%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Democratic-led%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20state%20attorneys%20general%20have%20said%20that%20the%20understanding%20of%20the%20Constitution's%20citizenship%20clause%20was%20cemented%20127%20years%20ago%20when%20the%20U.S.%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20that%20children%20born%20in%20the%20United%20States%20to%20non-citizen%20parents%20are%20entitled%20to%20American%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2014th%20Amendment%20was%20adopted%20in%201868%20following%20the%20Civil%20War%20and%20overturned%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20notorious%201857%20Dred%20Scott%20decision%20that%20had%20declared%20that%20the%20Constitution's%20protections%20did%20not%20apply%20to%20enslaved%20Black%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Justice%20Department%20in%20its%20brief%20argued%20that%20the%2014th%20Amendment%20had%20never%20been%20interpreted%20to%20extend%20citizenship%20universally%20to%20everyone%20born%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%201898%20ruling%20in%20United%20States%20v.%20Wong%20Kim%20Ark%20concerned%20only%20children%20of%20permanent%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%20said%20the%20case%20by%20the%20four%20states%20also%20%26quot%3Bflunks%20multiple%20threshold%20hurdles.%26quot%3B%20The%20department%20said%20that%20only%20individuals%2C%20not%20states%2C%20can%20pursue%20claims%20under%20the%20citizenship%20clause%2C%20and%20that%20the%20states%20lack%20the%20necessary%20legal%20standing%20to%20sue%20over%20Trump's%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirty-six%20of%20Trump's%20Republican%20allies%20in%20the%20U.S.%20House%20of%20Representatives%20on%20Tuesday%20separately%20introduced%20legislation%20to%20restrict%20automatic%20citizenship%20to%20only%20children%20born%20to%20citizens%20or%20lawful%20permanent%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDT