2C%20we%20withdrew%20the%20component%20of%20the%20Punjab%20police%20in%20the%20security%20of%20Kejriwal%20ji%2C%26quot%3B%20Director%20General%20of%20Punjab%20Police%20Gaurav%20Yadav%20told%20reporters%20in%20Patiala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20showed%20our%20concerns%20to%20them.%20We%20will%20remain%20in%20touch%20with%20them.%20We%20will%20share%20our%20inputs%20with%20the%20Delhi%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20top%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%20for%20the%2070-member%20Delhi%20Assembly%20on%20February%205.%C2%A0The%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20February%208.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20a%20Z-plus%20protectee%2C%20has%20a%20comprehensive%20protection%20detail%20comprising%2063%20personnel%2C%20including%20a%20pilot%2C%20escort%20teams%2C%20close%20protection%20staff%20and%20search-and-frisk%20units.%20Additionally%2C%2015%20uniformed%20personnel%20from%20the%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPFs)%20are%20deployed%20for%20his%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2018%2C%20a%20stone%20was%20thrown%20at%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20car%2C%20which%20his%20party%20blamed%20on%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20the%20AAP%20leader%20was%20campaigning%20in%20his%20New%20Delhi%20constituency.%20The%20BJP%20claimed%20that%20the%20AAP%20leader's%20car%20hit%20two%20BJP%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20amid%20intelligence%20reports%20that%20a%20pro-Khalistan%20group%20is%20plotting%20an%20attack%20against%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BGod%20will%20save%20him%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20is%20destined%20to%20live%20as%20long%20as%20his%20%26quot%3Blifeline%26quot%3B%20allows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20at%20the%20time%20said%20they%20will%20review%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20security%20arrangements%20as%20there%20is%20speculation%20regarding%20a%20threat%20to%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp