l%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Feurovision-hamas-7-october-attack-survivor-to-represent-israel-13295072%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Feurovision-hamas-7-october-attack-survivor-to-represent-israel-13295072%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saif%20admitted%20to%20Lilavati%20by%20friend%20Afsar%20Zaidi%3A%20Hospital%20report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737656933000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117496538%2Cimgsize-30252.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsaif-ali-khan-was-attacked-at-2-30-am-admitted-to-lilavati-hospital-at-4-11-am-by-friend-afsar-zaidi-report%2Farticleshow%2F117496538.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117496538.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBollywood%20actor%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20was%20admitted%20to%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20around%20two%20hours%20after%20being%20stabbed%20multiple%20times%20at%20his%20Bandra%20West%20home.%20Various%20reports%20highlight%20discrepancies%20in%20how%20he%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20with%20accounts%20suggesting%20his%20manager%2C%20elder%20son%20Ibrahim%2C%20and%20an%20auto-rickshaw%20driver%20were%20involved.%20Saif%20showed%20remarkable%20composure%20despite%20his%20injuries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsaif-ali-khan-was-attacked-at-2-30-am-admitted-to-lilavati-hospital-at-4-11-am-by-friend-afsar-zaidi-report%2Farticleshow%2F117496538.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hungry%20And%20Thirsty%2C%20How%20Forces%20Gunned%20Down%2016%20Maoists%20In%20Chhattisgarh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20forces'%20supplies%20ran%20low%20and%20they%20were%20hungry%20and%20thirsty%2C%20but%20they%20didn't%20let%20that%20affect%20their%20morale%20and%20went%20on%20to%20kill%2016%20Maoists%2C%20including%20a%20senior%20leader%20carrying%20a%20Rs%201-crore%20bounty%2C%20in%20Kulhadighat%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Raipur%20district%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Raipur%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%20Amresh%20Mishra%20shared%20details%20of%20the%20encounter%2C%20revealing%20that%20the%20Maoists%20used%20drones%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20security%20forces.%20He%20said%20some%20of%20the%20Maoists%20killed%20carried%20a%20combined%20bounty%20of%20Rs%205%20crore%20and%20that%20the%20extremists%20likely%20lost%20more%20men%2C%20but%20may%20have%20carried%20away%20the%20bodies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInputs%2C%20Operation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20intelligence%20inputs%20revealed%20that%20a%20large%20group%20of%20senior%20Maoist%20cadres%20was%20assembling%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Kulhadighat.%20The%20group%2C%20reportedly%20comprising%2025-30%20prominent%20Maoist%20leaders%20from%20Odisha%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20cadres%2C%20had%20convened%20to%20discuss%20fund%20collection%2C%20panchayat%20elections%20and%20establishing%20a%20safe%20corridor%20from%20Bastar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20three%20phases%3A%20planning%2C%20tactical%20strategy%2C%20and%20monitoring.%20The%20security%20forces%2C%20equipped%20with%20precise%20intelligence%2C%20embarked%20on%20what%20they%20had%20thought%20would%20be%20an%20operation%20lasting%20a%20day%20and%20a%20half%2C%20which%20eventually%20stretched%20on%20for%20three%20days%20-%20until%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECombined%20teams%20of%20E-30%20soldiers%20(Gariaband%20district)%2C%20COBRA%20207%20and%20CRPF's%2065%20and%20211%20battalions%2C%20along%20with%20Odisha's%20Special%20Operations%20Group%20(SOG)%2C%20coordinated%20the%20tactical%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenging%20Terrain%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20unfolded%20in%20the%20rugged%20hills%20of%20Kulhadighat%2C%20with%20heavy%20firing%20exchanged%20between%20the%20security%20forces%20and%20the%20Maoists.%20Despite%20limited%20rations%20and%20gruelling%20conditions%2C%20the%20security%20personnel%20demonstrated%20unwavering%20resolve%20and%20high%20morale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspector%20General%20Mishra%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20security%20forces%20had%20initially%20set%20out%20for%20a%20one-and-a-half%20to%20two-day%20operation%2C%20but%20they%20ended%20up%20fighting%20the%20Naxalites%20for%20three%20days%2C%20while%20remaining%20hungry%20and%20thirsty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maoists%20he%20said%2C%20had%20also%20deployed%20two%20drones%20for%20surveillance%2C%20but%20the%20forces%20outmaneuvered%20them%20using%20local%20drones%20for%20intelligence%20and%20monitoring.%20The%20extremists%20were%20surrounded%20in%20a%20triangle-shaped%20ambush%2C%20with%20Odisha's%20Special%20Operations%20Group%20blocking%20escape%20routes%20to%20the%20state%2C%20and%20forces%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20covering%20the%20remaining%20exits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETop%20Leaders%20Neutralised%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%2016%20Naxals%20killed%2C%2011%20bodies%20have%20been%20identified%20and%20the%20biggest%20name%20of%20them%20all%20was%20Jayaram%20Reddy%20aka%20Chalapati%2C%20a%20Central%20Committee%20Member%2C%20who%20was%20a%20a%20key%20Maoist%20strategist%20and%20had%20been%20active%20since%201991.%20He%20was%20responsible%20for%20numerous%20attacks%2C%20including%20the%20killing%20of%20an%20MLA%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20played%20a%20central%20role%20in%20fund%20collection%20and%20urban%20Maoist%20propaganda.%20The%20government%20had%20announced%20a%20Rs%201%20crore%20reward%20for%20information%20leading%20to%20his%20arrest.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20others%20are%20Jayaram%20alias%20Guddu%2C%20a%20mobilisation%20expert%20with%20a%20notorious%20record%20of%20organising%20Maoist%20operations%20and%20Satyam%20Gawade%2C%20a%20top%20commander%20in%20Kanker%2C%20responsible%20for%20coordinating%20major%20operations%20over%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20leaders%20collectively%20carried%20a%20bounty%20exceeding%20Rs%205%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mishra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20emphasised%20that%20the%20elimination%20of%20these%20top%20leaders%20marks%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20Maoism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20killing%20of%20Chalapati%2C%20Guddu%2C%20and%20Gawade%20will%20cripple%20their%20network%20and%20strategies.%20We%20are%20on%20track%20to%20eradicate%20Maoism%20by%20March%202026%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20brighter%20future%20for%20Bastar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrategic%20Significance%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKulhadighat%2C%20a%20tribal-dominated%20region%20spread%20across%2075%20km%2C%20comprises%20seven%20villages%20surrounded%20by%20forests%20and%20hills.%20The%20area%20remains%20a%20no-network%20zone%2C%20with%20a%20population%20of%20about%201%2C500.%20Four%20of%20the%20villages%20are%20situated%20on%20hilltops%2C%20making%20accessibility%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20this%20region%20served%20as%20a%20strategic%20hub%20for%20Naxal%20leaders%20overseeing%20operations%20across%20Odisha%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20The%20rugged%20terrain%20and%20dense%20vegetation%20provided%20a%20natural%20shield%2C%20turning%20Kulhadighat%20into%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20Chalapati%20and%20other%20top%20cadre%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers%20in%20hilltop%20settlements%20lead%20secluded%20lives