0taxes%20of%20any%20nation%20on%20earth%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you%20don't%20make%20your%20product%20in%20America%2C%20which%20is%20your%20prerogative%2C%20then%20very%20simply%20you%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20tariff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20wide-ranging%20speech%2C%20Trump%20made%20a%20link%20between%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20oil%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20he%20would%20ask%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20Organization%20of%20the%20Petroleum%20Exporting%20Countries%20to%20bring%20down%20crude%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20price%20came%20down%2C%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20would%20end%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20leader%20then%20fielded%20question%20from%20the%20top%20executives%20of%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20Blackstone%20investment%20firm%2C%20Spanish%20group%20Banco%20Santander%20and%20French%20oil%20and%20gas%20giant%20TotalEnergies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20always%20a%20top%20draw%20in%20Davos%2C%20making%20waves%20at%20two%20previous%20in-person%20appearances%20during%20his%20first%20term%20in%202018%20and%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20showing%20up%20this%20year%20was%20tougher%20as%20the%20forum%20happened%20to%20start%20on%20the%20day%20of%20his%20inauguration%20in%20Washington%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScores%20stood%20in%20line%20to%20hear%20him%20speak.%20Some%20in%20the%20audience%20included%20European%20Central%20Bank%20chief%20Christine%20Lagarde%2C%20Polish%20President%20Andrzej%20Duda%20and%20Croatian%20Prime%20Minister%20Andrej%20Plenkovic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20fans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20Republican%20president's%20biggest%20cheerleaders%20on%20the%20world%20stage%2C%20Argentina's%20libertarian%20President%20Javier%20Milei%2C%20took%20the%20stage%20hours%20before%20Trump%2C%20delivering%20a%20fiery%20speech%20against%20%26quot%3Bthe%20mental%20virus%20of%20woke%20ideology%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilei%20said%20Argentina%20was%20%26quot%3Bre-embracing%20the%20idea%20of%20freedom%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthat%20is%20what%20I%20trust%20President%20Trump%20will%20do%20in%20this%20new%20America%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20praised%20like-minded%20leaders%20such%20as%20Trump%2C%20Italian%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20Hungarian%20Prime%20Minister%20Viktor%20Orban%20and%20El%20Salvador's%20President%20Nayib%20Bukele.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSlowly%20an%20international%20alliance%20has%20been%20formed%20of%20all%20those%20nations%20that%20want%20to%20be%20free%20and%20that%20believe%20in%20the%20ideas%20of%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20defended%20his%20%26quot%3Bdear%20friend%26quot%3B%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20billionaire%20and%20Trump%20ally%20caused%20a%20stir%20this%20week%20by%20making%20hand%20gestures%20at%20an%20inauguration%20event%20for%20the%20US%20president%20that%20drew%20comparisons%20to%20the%20Nazi%20salute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilei%20said%20Musk%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%2C%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bunfairly%20vilified%20by%20wokeism%20in%20recent%20hours%20for%20an%20innocent%20gesture%20that%20only%20means...%20his%20gratitude%20to%20the%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Let's%20not%20hyperventilate'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20already%20gave%20Davos%20a%20taste%20of%20what%20is%20to%20come%20since%20his%20inauguration%20on%20Monday%2C%20which%20coincided%20with%20the%20WEF's%20first%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20threatened%20tariffs%20on%20China%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%2C%20pulled%20the%20United%20States%20from%20the%20Paris%20climate%20pact%20and%20renewed%20his%20claim%20the%20Panama%20Canal%2C%20just%20to%20name%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20plans%20to%20cut%20taxes%2C%20reduce%20the%20size%20of%20the%20US%20federal%20government%20and%20deregulate%20industries%20likely%20found%20a%20sympathetic%20ear%20amongst%20many%20businesses%2C%20though%20economists%20warn%20the%20policies%20could%20rekindle%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20trade%20partners%20and%20rivals%20already%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20react%20in%20Davos%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20as%20they%20brace%20for%20a%20second%20round%20of%20his%20America%20First%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20invoking%20Trump's%20name%2C%20Chinese%20Vice%20Premier%20Ding%20Xuexiang%20warned%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20winners%20in%20a%20trade%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEuropean%20Commission%20president%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20said%20Brussels%20was%20ready%20to%20negotiate%20with%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20also%20underscored%20the%20European%20Union's%20diverging%20policy%20with%20him%20on%20climate%2C%20saying%20the%20bloc%20would%20stick%20by%20the%20Paris%20accord.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorld%20Trade%20Organization%20chief%20Ngozi%20Okonjo-Iweala%20called%20on%20cooler%20heads%20to%20prevail%20during%20a%20WEF%20panel%20discussion%20on%20tariffs%20on%20Thursday%2C%20warning%20that%20tit-for-tat%20levies%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bcatastrophic%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20world%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20let's%20not%20hyperventilate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20quipped.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20we%20are%20here%20to%20discuss%20tariffs.%20I've%20been%20saying%20to%20everybody%3A%20could%20we%20chill%2C%20also%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737656160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Ftfi0f8so_trump-davos-afp_625x300_23_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdona