-with-you%2Farticleshow%2F117496126.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fcbs-meteorologist-sam-kuffel-fired-after-criticizing-elon-musks-nazi-salute-i-dont-fk-with-you%2Famp_articleshow%2F117496126.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fcbs-meteorologist-sam-kuffel-fired-after-criticizing-elon-musks-nazi-salute-i-dont-fk-with-you%2Famp_articleshow%2F117496126.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saif%20Had%20Injuries%20In%205%20Places%2C%20Friend%20Took%20Him%20To%20Hospital%3A%20Medical%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20was%20stabbed%20in%20five%20places%20-%20back%2C%20wrist%2C%20neck%2C%20shoulder%2C%20and%20elbow%20-%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20an%20autorickshaw%20by%20his%20friend%20Afsar%20Zaidi%2C%20reveals%20the%20actor's%20medical%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20injuries%20range%20from%200.5%20cm%20to%2015%20cm%20in%20size.%20On%20the%20night%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20Saif's%20friend%20Afsar%20Zaidi%20took%20him%20to%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20at%204%3A11%20AM%20and%20completed%20the%20formalities%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20report%2C%20ending%20the%20speculation%20as%20to%20who%20accompanied%20the%20actor%20to%20the%20hospital%20on%20the%20night%20of%20the%20attack%20last%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bollywood%20actor%20was%20repeatedly%20stabbed%20in%20an%20apparent%20burglary%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20January%2016.%20His%20alleged%20attacker%20Sariful%20Islam%2C%20who%20had%20illegally%20entered%20India%20from%20Bangladesh%20last%20year%20and%20assumed%20the%20alias%20Bijoy%20Das%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20Saturday%20from%20Thane%20near%20Mumbai%20after%20a%20three-day%20manhunt%20involving%20at%20least%2020%20teams%20from%20the%20Mumbai%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%2C%2054%2C%20who%20has%20appeared%20in%20more%20than%2070%20movies%20and%20television%20series%2C%20was%20back%20home%20from%20the%20hospital%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20police%20has%20deployed%20two%20constables%20outside%20the%20Bandra%20residence%20of%20the%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20provided%20temporary%20police%20protection%20outside%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20Satguru%20Sharan%20building%20in%20Bandra%20West.%20Two%20constables%20from%20Bandra%20police%20station%20will%20be%20posted%20there%20in%20two%20shifts.%20CCTV%20cameras%20and%20widow%20grills%20have%20also%20be%20installed%20as%20part%20of%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20senior%20police%20official.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20has%20expressed%20his%20gratitude%20to%20autorickshaw%20driver%20Bhajan%20Singh%20Rana%2C%20who%20rushed%20him%20to%20the%20hospital%20on%20the%20night%20of%20the%20attack%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20people%20say%20that%20he%20(Saif)%20gave%20me%20Rs%2050%2C000%20or%20Rs%201%2C00%2C000%2C%20but%20I%20would%20not%20like%20to%20reveal%20the%20amount.%20He%20has%20requested%20me%20to%20not%20share%20this%20information%20and%20I'll%20keep%20my%20promise%20to%20him%2C%20whatever%20it%20is%2C%20it%20is%20between%20him%20and%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mr%20Rana%2C%20who%20shares%20a%20one-room%20flat%20in%20Khar%20with%20four%20other%20roommates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20autorickshaw%20driver%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20the%20actor%20and%20his%20family%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20shortly%20before%20Mr%20Khan%20was%20released%20from%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20met%20him%20(Saif)%20yesterday%20(Tuesday)%20at%20the%20hospital.%20He%20called%20to%20thank%20me%20for%20taking%20him%20to%20the%20hospital.%20He%20praised%20me.%20I%20got%20the%20blessings%20from%20him%20and%20his%20family.%20He%20(Khan)%20introduced%20me%20to%20his%20mother%20(Sharmila%20Tagore)%2C%20and%20I%20touched%20her%20feet.%20He