y%2C%20and%20his%20employer%20even%20rewarded%20him...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fakir%20went%20on%20to%20describe%20his%20son's%20life%20in%20India%2C%20painting%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20man%20simply%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20living%20in%20a%20foreign%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20salary%20in%20Mumbai's%20hotels%20is%20higher%20than%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20hotels%20there%20are%20quite%20large%2C%20and%20the%20salary%20is%20also%20higher%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fakir%20noted%2C%20suggesting%20that%20Shariful%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20better%20job%20prospects%20in%20the%20hospitality%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20accusations%20against%20his%20son%2C%20Fakir%20insists%20that%20he%20hasn't%20received%20any%20communication%20from%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20local%20police%20had%20contacted%20him%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20nothing%20like%20that%20has%20happened.%20No%20one%20has%20come%20from%20anywhere.%20We%20don't%20know%20anyone%20in%20India.%20We%20have%20no%20support%20in%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fakir%20reflected%20on%20his%20last%20conversation%20with%20Shariful%2C%20recalling%20their%20regular%20exchanges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20last%20conversation%20with%20my%20son%20was%20on%20a%20Friday%20evening%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Shariful)%20used%20to%20get%20his%20salary%20after%20the%2010th%20of%20every%20month...%20After%20that%2C%20he%20would%20talk%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737654300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fhdd80h7g_saif-attacker_650x400_19_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsaif-ali-khan-stabbing-man-on-cctv-d