ri%20Khan%2C%20where%20Chris%20Martin%20gave%20a%20shoutout%20to%20SRK.%20Meanwhile%2C%20SRK%20is%20set%20to%20start%20filming%20'King%2C'%20featuring%20Suhana%20Khan%20and%20Abhishek%20Bachchan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-holds-umbrella-for-son-abram-khan-on-their-latest-outing-as-they-twin-in-matching-black-outfits-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F117492975.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Took%20Dip%20At%20Sangam...%26quot%3B%3A%20Yogi%20Adityanath's%20Yamuna%20Dare%20To%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20on%20Thursday%20assailed%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20saying%20its%20government%20has%20turned%20Delhi%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bgarbage%20dump%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bden%20of%20chaos%26quot%3B%20while%20helping%20illegal%20Bangladeshis%20and%20Rohingyas%20to%20settle%20down%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20his%20first%20rally%20in%20the%20Kirari%20area%20for%20the%20February%205%20Delhi%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20Adityanath%20alleged%20that%20in%20a%20well-planned%20conspiracy%2C%20AAP%20deprived%20Delhiites%20of%20basic%20facilities%20and%20jeopardised%20national%20security%20with%20their%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20accused%20AAP's%20councillors%20and%20MLAs%20of%20being%20complicit%20in%20the%20entire%20plot%2C%20adding%20that%20AAP%20convener%20and%20former%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20committed%20the%20crime%20of%20converting%20the%20Yamuna%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bdirty%20drain%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20I%20along%20with%20all%20my%20ministers%20took%20a%20holy%20dip%20at%20the%20Sangam%20in%20Prayagraj%20where%20Maha%20Kumbh%20is%20on.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20Kejriwal%20whether%20he%20can%20bathe%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20in%20Delhi%20along%20with%20his%20ministers.%20He%20should%20answer%20if%20he%20has%20any%20moral%20courage%2C%26quot%3B%20CM%20Yogi%20said%20in%20Kirari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20alleged%20that%20the%20devotees%20and%20saints%20in%20holy%20Mathura-Vrindavan%20are%20also%20victims%20of%20AAP's%20%26quot%3Bsins%26quot%3B%20of%20AAP%20as%20%26quot%3BMother%20Yamuna%26quot%3B%20reaches%20there%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20dirty%20drain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20company%26quot%3B%20never%20cooperated%20for%20the%20cleanliness%20of%20the%20Yamuna%20under%20the%20Namami%20Gange%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20do%20not%20want%20to%20cooperate%20or%20undertake%20development%20works%20and%20provide%20basic%20facilities%2C%20Yogi%20charged.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20(AAP)%20only%20job%20is%20to%20spread%20lies%20and%20videos%20through%20social%20media%20and%20press%20conferences%20to%20mislead%20the%20people.%26quot%3B%20The%20UP%20chief%20minister%20held%20three%20rallies%20in%20Kirari%2C%20Karol%20Bagh%20and%20Janakpuri%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20dig%20at%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20CM%20Yogi%20said%20there%20is%20an%20%26quot%3BATM%20machine%20of%20lies%26quot%3B%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20slammed%20AAP%20alleging%20poor%20condition%20of%20roads%2C%20lack%20of%20sanitation%2C%20problems%20of%20drinking%20water%20and%20sewer%20overflows%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECM%20Yogi%20further%20claimed%20that%20the%20UP%20roads%20in%20Noida%20and%20Ghaziabad%20are%20far%20better%20than%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20per%20unit%20charge%20of%20electricity%20in%20UP%20for%20an%20ordinary%20consumer%20is%20not%20more%20than%20Rs%203-3.50%20while%20it%20is%20Rs%209-10%20per%20unit%20in%20Delhi.%20It%20means%20they%20(Delhi)%20are%20charging%20three%20times%20more%20money%20than%20UP%20but%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20provide%20a%2024-hour%20power%20supply%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogi%20Adityanath%20urged%20people%20to%20defeat%20those%20who%20are%20playing%20with%20them%2C%20making%20Delhi%20filthy%20and%20playing%20with%20national%20security.%20They%20have%20no%20right%20to%20come%20back%20to%20power%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcept%20for%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Council%20area%20where%20round-the-clock%20power%20supply%20is%20ensured%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20the%20power%20cuts%20in%20the%20remaining%20parts%20are%20more%20than%20in%20many%20other%20metros%20and%20cities%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20to%20form%20the%20double%20engine%20government%20of%20BJP%20and%20give%20Delhi%20a%20chance%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20beautiful%20cities%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20at%20CM%20Yogi%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20sought%20to%20know%20during%20an%20election%20rally%20how%20many%20hours%20power%20cut%20lasts%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20alleging%20poor%20governance%20under%20the%20saffron%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20just%20asked%20so%20many%20people%20and%20they%20are%20telling%20me%20that%20in%20Delhi%2C%20electricity%20is%20available%20for%2024%20hours.%20Our%20(AAP)%20government%20has%20been%20in%20Delhi%20for%2010%20years.%20We%20ensured%20that%20Delhi%20had%2024-hour%20electricity%20within%20just%205%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20BJP%20has%20been%20in%20power%20for%2010%20years%20with%20a%20double%20engine%20government.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20humbly%20ask%20Yogi%20ji%2C%20how%20many%20hours%20of%20power%20cuts%20occur%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20sarcastically%20at%20the%20rally%20in%20Delhi's%20Hari%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20another%20rally%20in%20Karol%20Bagh%2C%20CM%20Yogi%20accused%20the%20AAP%20leaders%20of%20settling%20Bangladeshi%20infiltrators%20in%20Okhla%20and%20other%20important%20places%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20office-bearers%20and%20MLAs%20had%20settled%20Bangladeshi%20infiltrators%20on%20the%20land%20of%20the%20irrigation%20department%20of%20the%20UP%20government%20around%20Jamia%20Nagar%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tried%20two%20to%20three%20times%20to%20explain%20that%20the%20land%20belonged%20to%20the%20UP%20government%20and%20when%20they%20forced%20their%20way%2C%20I%20had%20to%20send%20bulldozers%20from%20UP%20to%20remove%20them%20and%20get%20the%20land%20barricaded%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UP%20chief%20minister%20said%20he%20would%20provide%20land%20for%20any%20institution%20or%20facility%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20but%20would%20not%20give%20even%20one%20inch%20of%20land%20in%20Delhi%20for%20the%20foreign%20infiltrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlleging%20that%20AAP%20and%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20were%20betraying%20the%20country%2C%20CM%20Yogi%20said%20he%20believed%20Delhi%20people%20would%20no%20longer%20believe%20their%20misleading%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20is%20slated%20for%20a%20triangular%20contest%20between%20the%20ruling%20AAP%20and%20opposition%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20for%2070%20Assembly%20seats%20going%20to%20polls%20on%20February%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20will%20be%20declared%20after%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20on%20February%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737646740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fi2k2ip28_yogi-kejriwal_625x300_23_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-took-dip-at