0history.%20The%20two%20clashed%20during%20their%20time%20in%20IPL%20franchise%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders.%20Also%2C%20at%20the%202015%20Ranji%20Trophy%2C%20Bengal's%20Tiwary%20and%20Delhi's%20Gambhir%20had%20a%20heated%20argument%20during%20a%20game%20at%20the%20Feroz%20Shah%20Kotla%20ground.%20The%20incident%20was%20covered%20by%20every%20media%20house%20as%20it%20happened%20in%20broad%20daylight%20when%20the%20match%20was%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwary%20opened%20up%20on%20the%20fight%20and%20said%20that%20Gambhir%20also%20attacked%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sourav%20Ganguly%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F197-sourav-ganguly-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESourav%20Ganguly%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Tiwary%20said%20Gambhir%20gave%20him%20%3Cem%3E'ma-behen%20ki%20gali'%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20heard%20anybody%20give%20such%20abuses.%20If%20anybody%20abuses%20your%20mother%2C%20you%20should%20not%20take%20it%20lying%20down.%20I%20am%20not%20a%20person%20who%20can%20handle%20abuses%20quietly.%20I%20asked%20him%2C%20'Gauti%20bhai%2C%20why%20are%20you%20talking%20like%20this%3F'.%20Then%20the%20over%20got%20over.%20Then%20I%20lost%20cool.%20He%20said%2C%20'meet%20me%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20I%20will%20thrash%20you'.%20I%20said%2C%20'why%20evening%3F%20let's%20do%20it%20now.'%20The%20match%20was%20in%20Delhi.%20No%20player%20ever%20talked%20to%20me%20in%20that%20way.%20All%20media%20persons%20present%20heard%20all%20the%20words%20that%20came%20out%20from%20his%20mouth%2C%26quot%3B%20Tiwary%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelallantop.com%2Flallankhas%2Fvideo%2Fex-cricketer-manoj-tiwary-interview-in-baithaki-talks-about-gautam-gambhir-dhoni-ganguly%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELallantop%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUmpire%20came%20in%20between%20and%20he%20pushed%20away%20him%20too.%20Then%20the%20over%20ended%20and%20I%20was%20at%20the%20non-striker's%20end.%20He%20came%20to%20mid-off%20and%20started%20abusing%20me%20again.%20Umpires%20can't%20do%20much.%20He%20is%20a%20big%20player%2C%20and%20they%20are%20afraid%20that%20he%20can%20use%20his%20influence%20against%20them.%20Then%20Sourav%20Ganguly%20was%20new%20to%20the%20Board.%20He%20started%20talking%20absolute%20non-sense%20about%20Sourav%20Ganguly.%20He%20accused%20him%20of%20using%20'source'%20to%20enter.%20He%20even%20said%20that%20'you%20are%20doing%20the%20same%20thing'.%20He%20said%20this%20at%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20you%20tell%20Sourav%20Ganguly%20about%20the%20incident%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20anchor%20asked%20Tiwary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20said%20'%3Cem%3Ethik%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E'...the%20way%20he%20speaks%2C%20'%3Cem%3Edekhta%20hu%3C%2Fem%3E'.%20My%20job%20was%20to%20tell%20him.%20I%20think%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20has%20anger%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Tiwary%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20Gambhir's%20contract%20with%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20as%20coach%20may%20be%20reviewed%20after%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737645240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fjfj9n47g_gautam-gambhir-sourav-ganguly_625x300_23_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-spoke-absolute-nonsense-about-sourav-ganguly-ex-teammate-accuses-this-was-dadas-reply-7542831%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir's%20contract%20with%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20as%20coach%20may%20be%20reviewed%20after%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-spoke-absolute-nonsense-about-sourav-ganguly-ex-teammate-accuses-this-was-dadas-reply-7542831%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%