ladesh%20last%20year%20and%20assumed%20the%20alias%20Bijoy%20Das.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESariful%2C%2030%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20Saturday%20from%20Thane%20near%20Mumbai%20after%20a%20three-day%20manhunt%20involving%20at%20least%2020%20teams%20from%20the%20Mumbai%20Police.%20He%20was%20produced%20in%20court%20the%20next%20day%20and%20has%20been%20in%20police%20custody%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20police%20officials%20said%20that%20while%20they%20already%20knew%20that%20Shariful%20was%20Bangladeshi%2C%20they%20have%20now%20found%20evidence%20in%20the%20form%20of%20two%20identity%20cards%20in%20his%20name%20from%20the%20country.%20The%20first%20is%20a%20National%20Identity%20Card%20which%20states%20that%20Shariful%20was%20born%20on%20March%203%2C%201994%2C%20and%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Mohammed%20Ruhul%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20document%20is%20a%20learner's%20driver's%20licence%20which%20reveals%20that%20Shariful%20was%20a%20resident%20of%20Barisal%2C%20a%20city%20in%20south-central%20Bangladesh.%20The%20licence%20was%20issued%20in%20November%202019%20and%20was%20supposed%20to%20expire%20in%20February%202020.%20The%20date%20for%20his%20written%2C%20oral%20and%20practical%20test%20for%20a%20permanent%20licence%20was%20set%20for%20March%2018%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaif%20Ali%20Khan%20was%20stabbed%20six%20times%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20January%2016%2C%20allegedly%20by%20Sariful%2C%20who%20had%20entered%20the%20actor's%20house%20in%20the%20'Satguru%20Sharan'%20building%20in%20Bandra%20West%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20carrying%20out%20a%20theft.%20Sariful%20had%20demanded%20Rs%201%20crore%20from%20the%20nanny%20of%20Saif's%20three-year-old%20son%20Jehangir%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Jeh%2C%20and%20stabbed%20Mr%20Khan%20when%20he%20confronted%20him%20and%20grabbed%20hold%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Entry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20had%20earlier%20said%20Shariful%2C%20who%20has%20studied%20till%20class%2012%2C%20had%20entered%20India%20through%20Meghalaya%20seven%20months%20ago%20and%20stayed%20in%20West%20Bengal%20for%20some%20time.%20He%20changed%20his%20name%20to%20Bijoy%20Das%20to%20avoid%20suspicion%20and%20used%20a%20local%20resident's%20Aadhaar%20card%20to%20get%20a%20mobile%20phone%20SIM%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2030-year-old%20then%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Mumbai%20to%20search%20for%20a%20job%20and%20initially%20worked%20in%20places%20where%20he%20was%20not%20required%20to%20produce%20any%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20had%20said%20that%20after%20he%20was%20caught%2C%20Shariful%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20was%20the%20one%20who%20had%20attacked%20Mr%20Khan%20and%20he%20had%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EHaan%2C%20maine%20hi%20kiya%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(yes%2C%20it%20was%20me).%26quot%3B%20He%20will%20be%20produced%20in%20court%20again%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaif%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20who%20suffered%20severe%20injuries%20-%20including%20to%20his%20spine%20-%20was%20discharged%20from%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%2054-year-old%20actor%20will%20now%20have%20a%20police%20constable%20staying%20with%20him%20around%20the%20clock%20and%20he%20will%20also%20use%20the%20services%20of%20a%20security%20firm%20run%20by%20fellow%20actor%20Ronit%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737644400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F8t9nah68_saif-attacker-identity-card-sariful-islam_625x300_23_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsaif-ali-khan-sariful-islam-shariful-islam-mumbai-id-card-learners-licence-cops-get-proof-saif-attacker-is-bangladeshi-7542800%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Mumbai%20Police%20teams%20investigating%20the%20stabbing%20of%20actor%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20have%20accessed%20two%20identity%20cards%20proving%20the%20nationality%20of%20his%20alleged%20attacker%20Sariful%20Islam%2C%20who%20had%20illegally%20entered%