f%20neither%20parent%20holds%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20-%20which%20has%20already%20been%20contested%2C%20in%20separate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-judge-to-hear-states-bid-to-block-trump-birthright-citizenship-order-7540898%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuits%20filed%20by%20a%20coalition%20of%2022%20states%20and%20civil%20rights%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20was%20the%20opening%20shot%20in%20what%20will%20likely%20be%20a%20flurry%20of%20laws%20that%20will%20alter%2C%20dramatically%2C%20the%20United%20States'%20immigration%20landscape%2C%20which%20was%20what%20Trump%20promised%20his%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20how%20that%20landscape%20will%20change%20is%20anybody's%20guess%3B%20Trump's%20flurry%20will%20also%20include%20a%20clampdown%20on%20what%20the%20Republican%20has%20said%20as%20illegal%20immigration%20along%20the%20southern%20border%2C%20i.e.%2C%20with%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20impact%20-%20on%20Indian%20families%20living%20in%20that%20country%2C%20specifically%20those%20on%20temporary%20H1B%20or%20L1%20visas%2C%20which%20do%20not%20grant%20permanent%20residency%20-%20is%20already%20being%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20C-Section%20Rush%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20and%20gynaecologists%20in%20the%20US%20are%20reporting%20a%20sudden%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20pregnant%20Indian%20women%2C%20on%20such%20visas%2C%20asking%20for%20a%20caesarean%2C%20to%20ensure%20pre-term%20delivery%20of%20their%20children%3B%20i.e.%2C%20before%20February%2020%2C%20which%20is%20when%20Trump's%20new%20mandate%20goes%20into%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rush%20is%20because%20children%20born%20before%20that%20date%20will%20be%20granted%20citizenship%2C%20while%20those%20born%20after%20will%20not%2C%20subject%20to%20one%20big%20condition%20-%20they%20will%20only%20become%20citizens%20if%20at%20least%20one%20parent%20is%20already%20a%20citizen%20or%20a%20Green%20Card%20holder.%20If%20not%2C%20then%20out%20they%20go%2C%20when%20they%20turn%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20beat%20that%2C%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frush-for-preterm-babies-to-beat-birthright-citizenship-deadline%2Farticleshow%2F117470382.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20Dr%20SD%20Roma%20in%20New%20Jersey%20as%20saying%20the%20majority%20of%20women%20lining%20up%20for%20a%20caesarean%20are%20in%20their%20eighth%20or%20ninth%20month%20of%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20seven-month%20pregnant%20woman%20came%2C%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20a%20pre-term%20delivery.%20She%20isn't%20due%20until%20sometime%20in%20March%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20medical%20professional%2C%20Dr%20SG%20Mukkala%2C%20an%20obstetrician%20and%20gynaecologist%20in%20Texas%2C%20said%20he%20has%20been%20advising%20similarly%20desperate%20couples%20of%20the%20dangers%20of%20a%20pre-term%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComplications%20include%20underdeveloped%20lungs%2C%20feeding%20problems%2C%20low%20birth%20weight%2C%20neurological%20complications%2C%20and%20more...%20in%20the%20past%20two%20days%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%2015-20%20couples%20about%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20The%20Panic%20For%20Indians%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20panic%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20Indians%20in%20the%20US%20on%20H1B%20or%20L1%20visas%2C%20of%20whom%20there%20are%20several%20lakhs%2C%20had%20anticipated%20being%20able%20to%20reside%20there%20for%20decades%20and%20have%20children%2C%20who%20would%20automatically%20become%20American%20citizens.%20But%20now%20that%20door%20is%20slowly%20swinging%20shut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-donald-trumps-day-1-order-to-end-birthright-citizenship-will-impact-indians-7525045%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20Trump's%20Day%201%20Order%20To%20End%20Birthright%20Citizenship%20Will%20Impact%20Indians%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20won't%20impact%20Green%20Card%20holders%2C%20whose%20children%20can%20still%2C%20even%20after%20Feb%2020%2C%20be%20born%20as%20American%20citizens%2C%20but%20the%20waiting%20list%20for%20that%20oh-so%20valuable%20piece%20of%20paper%20is%20long%2C%20very%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20a%20million%20Indians%20are%20reportedly%20stuck%20in%20that%20queue%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20new%20about%20if%2C%20or%20when%2C%20many%20of%20those%20applications%20will%20be%20processed%20and%20that%20list%20reduce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20it%20will%20impact%20is%20the%20children%20of%20Indians%20living%20on%20work%20visas%2C%20who%20will%20either%20have%20to%20self-deport%2C%20i.e.%2C%20voluntarily%20return%20to%20their%20home%20nation%2C%20or%20apply%20for%20a%20visa%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20it%20will%20further%20impact%20is%20the%20entire%20family%2C%20since%20many%20will%2C%20naturally%2C%20elect%20to%20return%20with%20their%20children.%20Trump%20has%20acknowledged%20this%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20break%20up%20families%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20also%20declaring%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20only%20way%20you%20don't...%20(is%20by)%20sending%20them%20all%20back%26quot%3B%2C%20suggesting%20there%20is%20no%20backdoor%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Birthright%20Citizenship%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20born%20in%20the%20US%20is%20considered%20a%20citizen%20at%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20derives%20from%20the%20Citizenship%20Clause%20of%20the%2014th%20Amendment%2C%20which%20was%20added%20to%20the%20Constitution%20in%201868.%20The%20amendment%20states%3A%20%26quot%3BAll%20persons%20born%20or%20naturalized%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20subject%20to%20the%20jurisdiction%20thereof%2C%20are%20citizens%20of%20the%20United%20States%20and%20of%20the%20State%20wherein%20they%20reside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEXPLAINED%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-what-is-us-birthright-citizenship-and-can-trump-end-it-7286384%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhat%20Is%20US%20Birthright%20Citizenship%20And%20Can%20Trump%20End%20It%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20an%20estimated%2013-14%20million%20immigrants%20living%2C%20illegally%2C%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20their%20children%2C%20if%20born%20in%20that%20country%2C%C2%A0are%20considered%20American%20citizens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20Trump%20Do%20This%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20president%20has%20ever%20tried%20to%20redefine%20the%20rules%20of%20citizenship%20using%20executive%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Trump's%20attempt%20to%20make%20history%20has%20put%20him%20on%20a%20collision%20course%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%2C%20if%20that%20course%20holds%2C%20a%20landmark%20decision%20on%20who%20can%2C%20and%20who%20cannot%2C%20be%20an%20American%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20courts%20decide%20to%20protect%20'birthright%20citizenship'%2C%20then%20only%20an%20amendment%20can%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20amendment%20would%20require%20two-thirds%20of%20both%20houses%20and%20approval%20by%20three-quarters%20of%20state%20legislatures%2C%20a%20process%20that%20will%20likely%20take%20years%2C%20and%20that%20is%20something%20of%20which%20Trump%20will%20be%20aware.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20then%2C%20is%20set%20to%20be%20a%20very%20long-term%20game%2C%20one%20that%20might%20extend%20beyond%20his%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Constitution%20has%20not%20been%20amended%20since%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3