ant%20women%2C%20including%20Jhili%2C%20during%20a%20vulnerable%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBridging%20the%20diagnostic%20gap%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20extensive%20field%20visits%20and%20review%20meetings%20after%20his%20joining%20in%20July%202022%2C%20Dibyajyoti%20found%20a%20critical%20lack%20of%20ultrasound%20facilities%20in%20rural%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20gap%20left%20many%20pregnant%20women%20without%20access%20to%20the%20necessary%20ultrasounds%20during%20their%20nine-month%20gestation%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20District%20Collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20diagnostic%20services%20were%20concentrated%20mostly%20in%20urban%20areas%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20remotely%20placed%20villages%20to%20access%20these%20services.%20This%20motivated%20us%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20and%20use%20technology%20for%20a%20real-time%20assessment%20of%20diagnostic%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-1-1737031907.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Ganjam%20district%20administration%20launched%20the%20Nirikhyana%20scheme%20to%20offer%20free%20USG%20services%20to%20pregnant%20women.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-1-1737031907.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-1-1737031907-300x157.jpg%2